Synopsis of the genus Corythaica St√•l (Insecta, Heteroptera, Tingidae), with the description of three new species from ArgentinaIn the present contribution, three new species of the genus Corythaica from Argentina are described and illustrated: C. dellapei, C. leprosa and C. saltensis. Corythaica passiflorae is raised from synonymy with C. cyathicollis, and the identity of these species and C. monacha are discussed. An updated key to the Argentinean species of the genus is provided together with distributional maps and new records from Argentina.